==Event Maps==
[[File:Iris of Light and Dark - Map EN.png|500px|right]]

* The event maps are split, into corresponding normal and hard nodes, giving a total of 6 maps for normal mode and 6 maps for hard mode. [[File:CrestedMedallionPt.png|20px]] Iris Écus  are rewarded for defeating the boss at any map. <span style="color:red">Normal maps will have x3 [[File:CrestedMedallionPt.png|20px]] bonus for first clear each day.</span> This run also introduces [[Combat#Danger_Level|Danger Level]] and the Siren mechanic.

* On maps where you can see Siren fleets, there will be no Ambushes, Air Raids or Submarine enemies. Sirens variants can be DD, CL, CA, BB and CV. The Sirens will move on the map after you move a specific amount of times, based on YOUR fleet speed.

* Sirens have levels one below those of boss nodes. In addition, drops from Sirens are equivalent to drops from boss nodes, with the exception of boss-only drops such as SSR ships (i.e. Le Triomphant) and [[File:CrestedMedallionPt.png|20px]].

